<b>TK Soccer — Version 0.7.0 (Pre-Alpha)</b>

This update focuses on <b>progression, rewards, shop systems, 
premium content, UI polish, and significantly improved ball physics.</b>

<b>🎁 NEW: Player Progression & Reward System</b>

<b>🆙 Level-Up Rewards</b><br/>
• Players now earn <b>rewards when leveling up</b><br/>
• Milestone levels can grant <b>random cosmetic rewards</b><br/>
• Rewards are clearly displayed on a redesigned end screen

<b>🎉 New Reward Reveal Screen</b><br/>
• Brand-new <b>reward reveal animations</b> at the end of matches<br/>
Items now display:<br/>
• Rarity color backgrounds<br/>
• Rarity badges<br/>
• Improved title rendering<br/>
• Cleaner animations and transitions

<b>🎲 Random Item Drops</b><br/>
• Random rewards now use a <b>weighted rarity system</b><br/>
• Certain items are excluded from random drops to preserve rarity

<b>💰 Starting Economy Update</b><br/>
• New players now start with <b>500 Cash</b><br/>
• Economy and item ownership logic improved for reliability

<b>🛒 Shop & Premium Store Overhaul</b>

<b>🏪 Daily Rotating Shop</b><br/>
• Shop rotates items daily using improved calculation logic<br/>
• Weighted rarity system for fair rotation<br/>
• Ownership validation improved to prevent duplicate purchases

<b>💎 Premium Store Added</b><br/>
• New <b>Premium Store</b> for game passes and developer products<br/>
• Improved item previews with character model display<br/>
• Better hover effects and ownership indicators<br/>
• Cleaner confirmation dialogs with preview support

<b>🪙 Developer Product Support</b><br/>
Developer product purchases now:<br/>
• Process correctly<br/>
• Grant coins instantly<br/>
• Validate securely server-side

<b>👕 Customisation & Character Improvements</b>

<b>🔢 Kit Number System</b><br/>
• Players can now set their <b>Kit Number</b><br/>
• Includes increment/decrement UI and confirmation system<br/>
• Fully customizable

<b>🎭 Celebration Previews</b><br/>
• Celebrations can now be previewed in menu<br/>
• Improved visibility handling during cinematics<br/>
• Character properly restores after preview

<b>🧢 Accessory Cleanup</b><br/>
• Non-essential accessories removed on spawn for 
cleaner visuals and performance

<b>🎮 Controller & Input Improvements</b><br/>
• Improved <b>gamepad support</b><br/>
• D-Pad tool switching<br/>
• Proper PlayStation & Xbox input prompts<br/>
• Cleaner tool activation handling<br/>
• Refined set piece action bindings<br/>
• Free kick and penalty prompts now display correctly

